        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I hope that I will have a job in computer sciences in a society whether as a work in Belgium or in an other country. I may have a fiancee with whom I will live in a flat or a little house that we will praise. I would also like to have visit Japan once or twice... This is what I Imagine.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment">B1 sentence structure, A2 vocab</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment">It's difficult to assess because it is a short text.</note>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
        </body>
